pis.com/dsv-bucket/imgs/imgs/6c6b6717-6f98-40f2-a2d2-443478f3f02b.jpg","/hotels/golf",{"titles":39,"img":43,"link":44},[40,41,42],"THE BEST RESORT","โรงแรมของเรา","酒店","https://storage.googleapis.com/dsv-bucket/imgs/imgs/a114d25b-3c29-4ee8-823c-8eda8f8a1234.jpg","/hotels",{"titles":46,"img":51,"link":52},[47,48,49,50],"OUR EVENT","กิจกรรม","กิจกรรม CN","活動","https://storage.googleapis.com/dsv-bucket/imgs/imgs/06ddb0c1-ef4b-40ca-81d2-44cc3e4c0a77.jpg","/events",{"titles":54,"img":59,"link":60},[55,56,57,58],"BEST OFFER","ข้อเสนอของเรา","ข้อเสนอของเรา CN","优惠套餐","https://storage.googleapis.com/dsv-bucket/imgs/imgs/80bbd61f-cf61-4c24-9a03-21b8ecee31eb.jpg","/offer",{"titles":62,"img":67,"link":68},[63,64,65,66],"NEWS","ข่าว ","ข่าว CN","丹萨旺新聞","https://storage.googleapis.com/dsv-bucket/imgs/imgs/5547ebfd-23dc-4cb0-9c4d-446d3a51c247.jpg","/news",[70],"https://storage.googleapis.com/dsv-bucket/imgs/imgs/02a04951-c778-4c05-9bb8-a85de0fb9fc9.jpg",[72,73,74],"DANSAVANH NAM NGUM RESORT","แดนสะหวันน้ำงึมรีสอร์ท","天湖（丹萨旺）国际旅游度假区",[76,77,78],"Dansavanh Nam Ngum Resort is located in the famous Nam Ngum Lake scenic spot in Laos, about 70 kilometers away from Vientiane city. Nam Ngum Lake  is the largest freshwater lake in Laos, covering an area of approximately 390 square kilometers. The lake is lined with islands, lush forests, strong biodiversity, and unique natural landscapes. It is a natural tourist resort.\nDansavanh Nam Ngum Resort  has a planned land area of 3,000 hectares and a land use life of 70 years. It is a key national tourism and cultural development project in Laos. Since its investment and development in 1996, it has completed the construction of Dansavanh Hotel\nSwan Lake Hotel, Dansavanh Golf and Country Club, Dansavanh International Entertainment City, Dansavanh Yacht Club, Vientiane Dansavanh Hotel and other projects, and has initially formed a brand and scale in Singapore. , South Korea, Thailand, Malaysia and other Southeast Asian tourism markets have good brand awareness.\n     The planning and development of Dansavanh Nam Ngum Resort  will focus on the development and protection of  Nam Ngum Lake tourism resources, and build a cultural landscape display area, commercial tourism service area, and natural ecological reserve around the south bank ofNam Ngum Lake. Nam Ngum Lake is built to become a world-class tourist destination and a Southeast Asian tourism and cultural center. In order to achieve this goal, we will welcome more powerful and experienced tourism and entertainment companies to participate in the investment and construction of Tianhu International Tourism Resort with an open mind and enthusiastic service, and share the development results.","ตั้งอยู่ในเมืองเวียงจันทน์ ขับรถ 5 นาทีถึงสนามบินนานาชาติวัตไต และ 10 นาทีถึงใจกลางเมืองและตลาดกลางคืน ทำให้ที่นี่เป็นสถานที่ยอดนิยมสำหรับนักเดินทางจำนวนมาก มีห้องจัดเลี้ยงที่สามารถรองรับคนได้ 800 คน และมีการเฉลิมฉลองงานแต่งงานมากมาย","天湖国际旅游度假区位于老挝著名的天湖（又名南俄湖）风景名胜区，距离万象市区约70公里。天湖（南俄湖）是老挝境内最大的淡水湖泊，面积约为390平方公里，湖内岛屿林立，森林茂盛，生物多样性强，自然景观奇特，是天然的旅游度假胜地。\n　　天湖国际旅游度假区规划用地面积为3000公顷，土地使用年限为70年，是老挝国家重点旅游文化发展项目。自1996年投资开发以来，已经完成了天湖国际度假村酒店、天湖高尔夫乡村俱乐部、天湖国际娱乐城、天湖游艇俱乐部、万象天湖酒店等项目的建设，初步形成品牌和规模，在新加坡、韩国、泰国、马来西亚等东南亚旅游市场具有较好的品牌知名度。\n　　天湖国际旅游度假区的规划和发展，将以天湖（南俄湖）旅游资源的开发和保护为核心，围绕天湖南岸建设人文景观展示区、商业旅游服务区、自然生态保护区，把天湖建设成为世界一流的旅游目的地和东南亚旅游文化中心。为实现这一目标，我们将以开放的心态、热情的服务，欢迎更多有实力、有经验的旅游娱乐企业共同参与天湖国际旅游度假区的投资建设，共享发展成果。",[80,81,82,83,84,85,86,87,88,89,90,91,92,93,94,95,96,97,98,99,100,101,102,103,104,105,106,107,108,109,110,111,112,113,114,115,116,117,118,119,120,121,122,123,124,125,126],"https://storage.googleapis.com/dsv-bucket/imgs/imgs/63398983-67a8-4283-bad5-c1977e919986.jpg","https://storage.googleapis.com/dsv-bucket/imgs/imgs/9f035e61-2c45-4f25-83be-7c164791b59d.jpg","https://storage.googleapis.com/dsv-bucket/imgs/imgs/afdf91ee-2232-4858-bd30-e8b27e32b99b.jpg","https://storage.googleapis.com/dsv-bucket/imgs/imgs/9c7e8149-adfb-4e66-a11d-50416b65a73c.jpg","https://storage.googleapis.com/dsv-bucket/imgs/im